name: Books Galore - Angular Example
body:
### Design

The is a simple app made using CSS3, HTML, and AngularJS.
It makes the use of directives and services to display information on the webpage. The code is available on GitHub.


### Authors and Contributors
The images of the books used, do not belong to me and belong to their rightful owners. I've only written the code to display the workings of AngularJS.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
